   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>1</fr:month><fr:day>30</fr:day></fr:date><fr:anchor>7319</fr:anchor><fr:addr type="machine">unstable/6083</fr:addr><fr:route>unstable-6083.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="" /><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\colon  B\to  A]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="jms-00KS.xml" title="Section-retraction pair" addr="jms-00KS" type="local">section</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex>. Fixing <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b_1,b_2\in  B]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s{\mathopen {}\left (b_1\right )\mathclose {}}=s{\mathopen {}\left (b_2\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>, we must show that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b_1=b_2]]></fr:tex>. We have <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r{\mathopen {}\left (s{\mathopen {}\left (b_1\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}=r{\mathopen {}\left (s{\mathopen {}\left (b_2\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> by assumption, and thus <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b_1=r{\mathopen {}\left (s{\mathopen {}\left (b_1\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}=r{\mathopen {}\left (s{\mathopen {}\left (b_2\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}=b_2]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
